item.title: How do i make it were i can
item.dc:creator: @Liam1 Liam-
item.description:
@Liam1 wrote:

alrighty, right click the screen, and select new folder, type in Characters, then when a person logs in or out, it should save there, unless the paths are set off, then go to that player character, scroll down to “player rights= 0” and replace with 1 for mod 2 for admin 3 for owner and 4 for invisible owner

hope this helped,

-Liam
